1. incorporation of discount in print new bill & reprint bill 2. changes for printing business date in bill. Earlier it was printing tab's date.

changes for saving time correctly in database during billing

1 reportHandler.java -> displaying reports within given date range 2. countersales.java/xml -> displaying date when current date is not same as business date save time properly in database while billing 3. homeDeliveryBillingScreen.java/xml -> displaying date when current date is not same as busineess date
1. correcting display of petty cash customers in activity_customerdetail.xml
1. paybillActivity.java - displaying amount to recieved in toast
1. paybillActivity.java - displaying amount to recieved in toast even when entered amount is less than the total bill amount.
1. ConvertIngredientAcitvity.java - displaying units along with quantity in toast when required ingredient quantity is less then available quantity.
